    "part_title": "MISCELLANEOUS",
    "title": "Inspection  of  plans.",
    "content": "(1)  An  approved  plan  may  be  inspected  in  the  office  of  the  local  authority  subject  to  the  payments of  the  prescribed  fee. (2)  An  approved  plan  may  be  copied  in  the  office  of  the  local  authority  subject  to  the  applicant submitting with his application to copy such plan the written consent of the owner of the building. (3)  The  fees  payable  shall  be  as  follows: (i)for inspecting an approved plan         ..         .. RM100.00 per set of plans. (ii)for copying an approved plan    ..       ..         ..RM200.00 per set of plans. [Amendment  2012] (4) The fee for an endorsement by the local authority to certify any copy as a true copy of an approved plan  shall  be  RM100.00  per  copy. [Amendment  2012]",
